{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "原初之力 第24章 3-1 父亲的决断",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "不毁灭女儿的灵魂就无法继续前进。\\n迦道夫对此感到错愕。经过一夜的烦恼，\\n迦道夫决定进入黑暗魔力之中拯救女儿。\\n然而席菈的灵魂却唤来了魔兽，\\n迦道夫以必死的决心迎战。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈的灵魂……在这瘴气深处？\\n勒福克斯的黑暗魔力\\n是席菈召唤来的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，\\n席菈的灵魂确实是这么说的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你竟然一点都不惊讶？\\n是有些什么头绪吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "有一天，王都内突然涌入了\\n与以往无法比拟的大量的黑暗魔力。\\n勒福克斯陷入一片恐慌之中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "当时我并不知道那究竟是怎么回事，\\n更不明白是什么导致的。\\n听了你说的，我才终于明白。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "勒福克斯还没能来得及应对\\n那黑暗魔力就已经被敌国攻陷，\\n我的妻子和席菈也就此丧命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "所以你才会为了复活女儿\\n而前往精灵国对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯，没错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但精灵王芬罗达\\n却没能完美复活席菈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芬罗达以魔神为基础制造的肉体\\n并不适合席菈的灵魂。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "灵魂承受不了魔神肉体的污秽，\\n被肉体所排斥，\\n最终在世间彷徨。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "结果就是席菈失去了心。\\n这就是至今为止事情的经过吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "一般来说，脱离肉体的灵魂会化为魔力\\n但席菈的灵魂却留在了这片土地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "看来她相当挂念\\n自己的祖国啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "席菈学会了控制黑暗魔力。\\n即使现在只剩下灵魂，\\n也在不断地召唤着黑暗魔力……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "难道说……席菈是刻印之器？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "刻印之器……\\n也就是说席菈也是巫女吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "现在还不能确定，\\n但确实有这个可能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "巫女是“起始之人”的仿制品，\\n拥有与异界沟通的能力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "如果席菈是拥有接受“原始刻印”\\n资质的巫女的话，也正好能解释\\n为什么她可以控制黑暗魔力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "原来如此。确实有道理……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈的灵魂与肉体分离后，\\n就一直在这里为自己的\\n所作所为而忏悔吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "席菈的灵魂似乎已经\\n彻底与黑暗魔力同化。\\n根本没法进行沟通……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "彻底与黑暗魔力同化……\\n也就是说……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我们已经没有办法将她的灵魂\\n从黑暗魔力中剥离出来了吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "话虽如此，但我们如果不想办法\\n处理席菈那不断召唤黑暗魔力的灵魂，\\n就根本无法抵达龙之墓……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我听说你至今为止都一直在\\n为恢复女儿的心而奔波。\\n但如今事已至此，你也只能放弃了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "放弃她的灵魂继续前进，\\n寻找打倒泽诺斯的办法。\\n这是理所当然的选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "奈迪犹。\\n你好歹考虑一下\\n迦道夫的心情……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但确实有这个必要。\\n当然，我不会说让你亲自下手。\\n自会有人来处理，你想恨就尽管恨吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "有这个必要……吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "迦道夫，就算我们到了龙之墓，\\n也不能保证一定能找到\\n打倒泽诺斯的方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "即便牺牲席菈的灵魂继续前进，\\n结局也有可能是一无所获。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "希望你能在此基础之上\\n做出不会让自己后悔的选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "无论你做出怎样的决定，\\n我们都会接受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯……\\n能让我和席菈单独待一会儿吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们先离开这里吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（若要阻断黑色魔力，\\n就必须要毁掉席菈的灵魂。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（但那样一来，\\n席菈的心就再也回不来了。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈……\\n我究竟该如何选择啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "呼……呼……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……\\n勒福克斯还……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "勒福克斯已经沦陷了。\\n都怪我没有本事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "这不怪爸爸……\\n爸爸不是已经为了\\n守护大家而奋战了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "您是我……值得骄……傲的……\\n父亲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（席菈是个好孩子，\\n至死都还在为国家着想。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（她一定不会为了自己的性命\\n而不惜成为危害祖国的存在。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（我明白的。无论是当时复活席菈，\\n还是如今我的犹豫不决，\\n都是我的自私在作祟。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（一切都是源于我的软弱。\\n一切都是因为我不想在\\n失去国家之后再失去心爱的女儿。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "对不起……\\n是我的自私让你如此痛苦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "如果，我现在开始努力做个\\n值得你骄傲的父亲，还来得及吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你已经决定了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯。尤蒂尔，\\n你能带我去席菈灵魂所在之地吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01",
                "100009_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "危险。以人类之躯踏入那\\n高浓度的黑暗魔力之中\\n无异于自杀。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "即便如此我也必须要去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "为什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "因为我有比这条命\\n更加重要的东西。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "比生命更加重要的东西？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "当然是爱了。\\n非要让人家说明白就太不解风情了，\\n莱姬希。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你打算去那里做些什么呢，\\n迦道夫？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我想要尽我所能去解救\\n席菈的灵魂。话虽如此，\\n我也并非有什么具体的办法。",
